name: Jala Brat - Imperija
description: A game following Jala Brat's story. Level 1: Get to the Lambo. Level 2: Get your Lambo back in Sarajevo. Level 3: Record a hit song. Level 4: Get revenge on Grše & Peki. Level 5: Attend the funeral as Jala Mačeta. Level 6: Meet Siniša Vuco in Split. Level 7: After Vuco's betrayal, go to Ključ for one last hookah before the end.
